Title: Commending Highway Superintendent John Alonge, Harry Freeborn, Don Fredrick, and Police Chief Gerald Cocozza on their designation as recipients of a Liberty Medal
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION commending Highway Superintendent John Alonge, Harry Freeborn, Don Fredrick, Gary Lazaroff, and Police Chief Gerald Cocozzan upon the occasion of their designation as recipients of a Liberty Medal, the highest honor bestowed upon an individual by the New York State Senate
